{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1783429153613", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "关键发现：arXiv 2407.04219 (\"Semi-supervised Learning for Code-Switching ASR with Large Language Model Filter\") 以及 2305.13652 (\"Cross-lingual Knowledge Transfer and Iterative Pseudo-labeling for Low-Resource Speech Recognition\") —— 这些论文明确将迭代伪标签 (iterative pseudo-labeling) 技术应用到了语码转换 (code-switching) / 低资源 ASR 领域，直接反驳了本文关于“首次将迭代伪标签技术应用于语码转换 ASR”的声明。我来核实一下。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "170b038f-ba06-437a-b492-1b8075d6ac76", "uuid": "3db4be32-7419-45e4-b248-4f1b6f7776cb"}
